OL,5, A woman whose childhood pen pal        
OL,6, suddenly stopped writing after fleeing 
OL,7, the Rwanda genocide has written a novel
OL,8, to "exorcise the grief of not knowing  
OL,9, what happened" to her.                 
OL,11,FSophie Buchaillard's pen pal Victoria, 
OL,12,F16, was separated from her parents     
OL,13,Fwhile fleeing the 1994 genocide in     
OL,14,Fwhich an estimated 800,000 people were 
OL,15,Fkilled.                                
OL,17,FVictoria was staying at a refugee camp 
OL,18,Fin Goma, Democratic Republic of the    
OL,19,FCongo.                                 
